### Key Test Scenarios

**Database Layer**:
- âœ… Schema initialization (all 10 tables created)
- âœ… Pydantic validation (Field constraints enforced)
- âœ… Adapter conversion (Pydantic â†” SQLite)
- âœ… CRUD operations (create, read, update, delete)
- âœ… Foreign key validation (work_item_id exists)
- âœ… Transaction rollback (errors don't corrupt data)

**Workflow Management**:
- âœ… Time-boxing (IMPLEMENTATION >4h blocked)
- âœ… Required tasks (FEATURE needs DESIGN+IMPL+TEST+DOC)
- âœ… Forbidden tasks (PLANNING cannot have IMPLEMENTATION)
- âœ… Metadata validation (acceptance_criteria required)
- âœ… State transitions (only allowed transitions succeed)
- âœ… Dependency blocking (hard deps block task start)

**Plugins**:
- âœ… Framework detection (3-phase: files â†’ imports â†’ structure)
